com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management

Interface NetworksTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Networks
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NetworksStub

    public interface NetworksTypes
    The Networks interface provides lifecycle methods on vSphere Namespaces networks associated with a vSphere cluster. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.1.0.
